<Base title="Sutts — Privacy Policy">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Sutts — Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: 2026-05-05</p>

    <p>Sutts is built by BroooApps. This policy explains what data the app handles and how.</p>

    <h2>Data we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Habit logs</strong> — entries you create are stored locally on your device.</li>
      <li><strong>Anonymous usage analytics</strong> — to understand crashes and broad usage patterns. No personal identifiers.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data we do not collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name, email, phone number, or contacts.</li>
      <li>Your location.</li>
      <li>Your photos or files outside what you explicitly share with the app.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>AI features (Premium)</h2>
    <p>Premium AI features send the minimum necessary log data to Google's Gemini API for processing. Requests are not used to train models and are not stored beyond the immediate response.</p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>You can delete all app data at any time from the app's settings, or by uninstalling the app.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:swapniltiwari775@gmail.com">swapniltiwari775@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
